## Rule: Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS for all styling
- Follow utility-first conventions
- Mobile-first responsive design (no prefix → md: → lg:)
- DO NOT use inline styles
- DO NOT modify existing working CSS

## Rule: Component Patterns
- Extract repeated utilities with @apply for:
  - .btn-primary (CTA buttons)
  - .property-card (listings)
  - .hero-section (landing pages)